{"tid":1345252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方：不能確定身穿白衣人士就曾經參與打鬥","createTime":"2019-07-22T01:41:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T02:33:07.000Z","uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"3893dad81d524f1303faa91b5e7feed10542040e","tid":1345252,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:41:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%AD%A6-%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E7%A2%BA%E5%AE%9A%E8%BA%AB%E7%A9%BF%E7%99%BD%E8%A1%A3%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E5%B0%B1%E6%9B%BE%E7%B6%93%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%E6%89%93%E9%AC%A5-002235375.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%2583%25BD%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E5%25AE%259A%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E7%25A9%25BF%25E7%2599%25BD%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E6%259B%25BE%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%2589%2593%25E9%25AC%25A5-002235375.html&d=FZf2Eq7oNugCj0cVmX%2F%2FqXvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=9d73a509\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%AD%A6-%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E7%A2%BA%E5%AE%9A%E8%BA%AB%E7%A9%BF%E7%99%BD%E8%A1%A3%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E5%B0%B1%E6%9B%BE%E7%B6%93%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%E6%89%93%E9%AC%A5-002235375.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】元朗西鐵站及附近一帶，晚上有大批白衣人持籐條及木棍等武器追打市民，更加追打至月台及列車車廂。很多人被打至頭破血流，最少三十六人受傷求醫，其中一人危殆。<br />\n<br />\n警方解釋，首批到達元朗西鐵站的警員因為警力不足，所以未有即時阻止衝突，又指進入南邊圍村調查後未有拘捕任何人，因為看不到有人持攻擊性武器，亦不能夠確定身穿白衣的人士就曾經參與打鬥。<br />\n<br />\n有片段拍攝到，發生激烈衝突前，兩名警員離開元朗站，當時已經有白衣人在場。<br />\n<br />\n警方解釋說，是在星期日晚10時41分，接報有人受到刑事恐嚇，首批到場警員到場因為警力不足，未有即時制些衝突。<br />\n<br />\n其後白衣人退回南邊圍村內，警員進村調查期間有白衣人自行離開，警方解釋因為不能夠確定他們有參與打鬥。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，未發現有人持有攻擊性武器，否則會作出拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n咁多CCTV都拉唔到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家交錢仲要養呢班人"},{"pid":"a68cd15f082fba55713e0eed44f504e2d7fc5a74","tid":1345252,"uid":144942,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:41:50.000Z","msg":"啲狗盲咗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffd80400d818038c77ea7cc7b810a0e22c97473c","tid":1345252,"uid":3194,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:42:20.000Z","msg":"平時我地示威完者黑衫就check, 依家白衫就唔使check, 明哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1d889af366eb9122bb9be1621e3265617b419b8","tid":1345252,"uid":270577,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:42:27.000Z","msg":"咁身穿黑衣就係示威者，要抄牌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d54c1f0e975ee1b40a8b5a2dbd244aedd990bc7","tid":1345252,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:43:28.000Z","msg":"確定唔到就唔拉？<br />\n<br />\n咁中聯辦<br />\n你拉一個<br />\n即刻圍你"},{"pid":"2c08488255ba20b8ababab8945285b434a9ac287","tid":1345252,"uid":37003,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:44:21.000Z","msg":"信唔信昨日拎住開山刀都會話睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n昨日港頭村一大堆持刀咖啡仔但狗吠聲都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n街燈都停埋"},{"pid":"8e525298f2e8383df10bb901f49f542637ad39c7","tid":1345252,"uid":285514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:44:34.000Z","msg":"不能確定__智力正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"867888f5888afd99e11f888c67f68c85757a4534","tid":1345252,"uid":221696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:44:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/22/093123_9f7d9c7c1b682c47a5e249f59bbc821e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F22%2F093123_9f7d9c7c1b682c47a5e249f59bbc821e.png&h=d969c48e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49d1238bb5a3a8ab38e6a8d51de558271eaf362a","tid":1345252,"uid":228793,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":